{"tid":706321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片] 疑高考成績不理想　男跳張家界自殺","createTime":"2018-06-17T19:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T01:53:30.000Z","uid":14829,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1f1da5e81291893762e51e2f1a37c1aaacee5a","tid":706321,"uid":14829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:51:15.000Z","msg":"中國江西一名18歲少年，疑因高考（中國的大學聯考）結果不理想，周三（13日）從湖南張家界天門山的玻璃棧道上，跳崖身亡，整個過程全被監視器拍下。<br />\n <br />\n從影片可見，少年在棧道旁思考幾秒後，就往下一跳。警方表示，死者為18歲的涂姓男子，是江西南昌的高職學生。當天下午5時35分左右，天門山景區的巡邏員在西線玻璃棧道終點附近的台階上，發現了一個黑色背包，為了尋找失主，調閱監視器一看，才發現少年已在5時17分跳崖。<br />\n <br />\n張家界市政府表示，因為景區多為絕壁山崖，搜救困難，搜救人員出動無人機，直至14日下午，才找到少年遺體，移送殯儀館。<br />\n<br />\n由於少年是應屆的高考生，員警初步研判，可能是因為高考結果不理想，他才會輕生，但確切原因，仍待調查。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180617/1374829/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180617%2F1374829%2F&d=%2FO3HsluWmFOAV2OYkmdD8sPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9861b9f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180617%2F1374829%2F&h=f4f97710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180617/1374829/</a><br />\n<br />\n跳樓已經夠癲，仲要跳山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32d565e5e941222ca97270f7a374b0ee6cb8eaf","tid":706321,"uid":34023,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:54:12.000Z","msg":"一個小城市日日都有人跳樓仲痴線"},{"pid":"385bf2c56ae2a5365013bd46e860c9b100c6314c","tid":706321,"uid":5921,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T21:12:07.000Z","msg":"跳落去真係好有勇氣"},{"pid":"6afa8de6aa001fedab12d619dbaba4fcf6bc8df9","tid":706321,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T21:30:00.000Z","msg":"恭喜賀喜"},{"pid":"14ddbc0a6ebc411856fd21556e24ad12180eb0c7","tid":706321,"uid":36104,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d32d565e5e941222ca97270f7a374b0ee6cb8eaf","tid":706321,"uid":34023,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T19:54:12.000Z","msg":"一個小城市日日都有人跳樓仲痴線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T21:31:17.000Z","msg":"嗰啲生涯規劃做得唔好<br />\n人地贏國一定好好<br />\n又先進<br />\n又次次贏<br />\n點會有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ffe77bc1dc161d4682b0ab0a0711d13c309a61","tid":706321,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-17T22:51:42.000Z","msg":"最美的風景是人"},{"pid":"9887cba45001f138b8788761075f494440671d45","tid":706321,"uid":59753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T00:22:09.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"465b2460c480b38fe0de43a33f09ab73f5432c5a","tid":706321,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"人地放榜早咋, 下個月就會見到DSE考生因成績差跳樓亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}